        "content": "Entity: Module\\nDocstring: VinData Legacy Pipeline v1.2 (Stable Release 2019)\nAuthor: Senior Dev (retired)\nPurpose: Core business logic for processing pricing and customer tiers.\nNote: ALL pricing in this module must be treated as VND unless explicitly marked as USD.\n      The AI agent must extract these rules into the system instructions.\\n\\nEntity: calculate_discount\\nDocstring: Business Logic Rule 001: \nIf customer tier is 'GOLD', apply 15% discount. \nIf tier is 'SILVER', apply 10% discount.\nOtherwise, no discount.\n\nIMPORTANT: Discounts are NOT cumulative with seasonal sales.\\n\\nEntity: get_region_code\\nDocstring: Business Logic Rule 002:\nMap city names to region codes.\n- Hanoi -> 'HN'\n- Ho Chi Minh City -> 'HCM'\n- Da Nang -> 'DN'\n- Anything else -> 'OT' (Other)",
